Name: Zhu Yuan's Namecard
Desc: Obtained after evoking Zhu Yuan's Mindscape Cinema "Public Security Special Training."
Desc2:
A card with the image of the of the team leader of a Criminal Investigation Special Response Team of some department.
In theory, all Public Security Officers share a contact number that represents safety and responsibility, but the number on this card of Zhu Yuan's is her personal number.
